  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/894330/extras/27ca2aa0a8b07409b08d2730f1b5f7dc.avif?t=1765128180\" width=616 height=120 /></span><br>One Hunt is a challenging survival fps that forces you to stay on the move. In order to survive, you must collect sticks to create fires, find ammo for your shotgun, and avoid detection from various predators. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/894330/extras/44c98edc1af81b865b5c192144ca5fae.webp?t=1765128180\" width=616 height=60 /></span><br>Throughout the map are cabins that can keep you out of the cold and provide solace. They also contain useful items like snowshoes, ammo, and parkas.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/894330/extras/76a473bf0636bde77171daaee7ff511b.poster.avif?t=1765128180\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/894330/extras/76a473bf0636bde77171daaee7ff511b.webm?t=1765128180\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/894330/extras/76a473bf0636bde77171daaee7ff511b.mp4?t=1765128180\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Can you survive this hostile environment, or will your corpse be forever preserved by the permafrost?",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/894330/extras/27ca2aa0a8b07409b08d2730f1b5f7dc.avif?t=1765128180\" width=616 height=120 /></span><br>One Hunt is a challenging survival fps that forces you to stay on the move. In order to survive, you must collect sticks to create fires, find ammo for your shotgun, and avoid detection from various predators. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/894330/extras/44c98edc1af81b865b5c192144ca5fae.webp?t=1765128180\" width=616 height=60 /></span><br>Throughout the map are cabins that can keep you out of the cold and provide solace. They also contain useful items like snowshoes, ammo, and parkas.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/894330/extras/76a473bf0636bde77171daaee7ff511b.poster.avif?t=1765128180\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/894330/extras/76a473bf0636bde77171daaee7ff511b.webm?t=1765128180\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/894330/extras/76a473bf0636bde77171daaee7ff511b.mp4?t=1765128180\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Can you survive this hostile environment, or will your corpse be forever preserved by the permafrost?",
